title: S12 Ep96: Mojave Mysteries: Real Tales of Unknown Creatures, UFOs, Ghosts, Devil Cults, Giants & Mysterious Murders in the California Desert
itunes:title: Mojave Mysteries: Real Tales of Unknown Creatures, UFOs, Ghosts, Devil Cults, Giants & Mysterious Murders in the California Desert
description:
Author M.L. Behrman opens his cabinet of curiosities to bring us a deliciously spooky and bizarre collection of true accounts featuring everything from UFOs, unknown creatures, ghosts, hideous murders, demonic cults and some of the weirdest and most puzzling events ever to come out of the great Mojave Desert. This assortment of stories from witnesses, both modern and historical, detailing their encounters with things that left them shaken, terrified - or worse!
All that PLUS a new Theater of the Mind.
